lyrics:
Verse:
Under the neon lights, we move, Tokyo's calling (Ching Ching), in this groove,
Exploring streets, where samurais once roamed (ooo wee Banzai!),
In Kyoto's temples, where peace is home,
Mount Fuji's shadow, in the sunrise glow,
Sakura dances, as the cool winds blow. Chorus:
Vámonos, hermano, to the land of the rising sun (damn so hot), Singing bajo la luna, our adventure has just begun,
From the hustle of Shibuya to the calm of Nara's deer,
This journey with you, brother, brings the world so near.
